  <prompt>Update `appsettings.json` (`sdap-dev:` → `spaarke:`) + `appsettings.template.json` (verify `#{REDIS_INSTANCE_NAME}#` consumer documentation reflects `spaarke:` as the prescribed deploy-time value). Also check `Redis:InstanceName` default in `RedisOptions.cs` — already `"sdap:"`; change to `"spaarke:"`. Per FR-07.</prompt>
  <role>Spaarke .NET developer. Configuration changes only.</role>
  <goal>`grep -rn "sdap" src/server/api/Sprk.Bff.Api/` returns ZERO matches across all config + code.</goal>
